Level 4

You can hear bow strings being stretched.

Tip: No new abilities this time, but you must be careful not to rest while taking damage. Save a `_health` variable and compare it on each turn to see if you're taking damage.


 -------
|@ Sa S>|
 -------


  > = Stairs
  @ = hellsand (20 HP)
  S = Thick Sludge (24 HP)
  a = Archer (7 HP)


Warrior Abilities:

  Actions:
  
    warrior.rest()
      Gain 10% of max health back, but do nothing more.
  
    warrior.attack()
      Attacks a unit in given direction (forward by default).
  
    warrior.walk()
      Move in the given direction (forward by default).
  
  Senses:
  
    warrior.health()
      Returns an integer representing your health.
  
    warrior.feel()
      Returns a Space for the given direction (forward by default).
  

When you're done editing Player.js, run the warriorjs command again.
